data.description: This unique condo and rare opening at the Wheelock Building Downtown in the middle of all of the amazing restaurants and bars that the Loft District has to offer! This sunny corner TOP FLOOR loft has 11 foot ceilings, 22nd Street facing windows, gorgeous original wood floors, original exposed beams, exposed brick,& is perfectly designed for open living. This unit has raised bedroom which creates a true/open loft feel. When the weather turns cold, you can look forward to coming home and sitting in front of the wood burning fireplace to embrace the cooler weather! The building also offers one garage parking spot, extra storage, a roof top with a grill and dog run, & gym in the basement! Come check out this awesome unit for yourself!
